asilis Torosidis]]|pos=DF}} 20 (1)\n{{Fs player|no=77|nat=Slovenia|name=[[Mirnes \u0160i\u0161i\u0107]]|pos=MF}} 9 (2)\n{{Fs player|no=7|nat=Argentina|name=[[Luciano Galletti]]|pos=MF}} 13 (3)\n{{Fs end}}\n\n*Appearances (goals)\n\n==Competitions==\n\n===Overall===\n{{fb overall competition header |curr=y }}\n{{fb overall2 competition |bg=y |curr=y |cl = [[2008\u201309 Super League Greece|Super League Greece]]|cprn=1st |fp= |dfm=30 Aug 2008 |dlm=26 Apr 2009 }}\n{{fb overall2 competition |bg=  |curr=y |cl = [[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League|Champions League]]|srn = [[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League#Third qualifying round|Third qualifying round]]|fprn = [[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League#Third qualifying round|Third qualifying round]]|fp= |dfm=13 Aug 2008 |dlm=30 Aug 2008 }}\n{{fb overall2 competition |bg=y |curr=y |cl = [[2008\u201309 UEFA Cup|UEFA Cup]]|srn = [[2008\u201309 UEFA Cup#First round|First round]]|cprn = [[UEFA Cup 2008\u201309#Round of 32|Round of 32]]|fr=    |fp= |dfm=16 Sep 2008 |dlm= }}\n{{fb overall2 competition |bg=  |curr=y |cl = [[2008\u201309 Greek Football Cup|Greek Cup]]|srn=Round 4 |cprn=Round 5    |fr=    |fp= |dfm=29 Oct 2008 |dlm= }}\n{{fb overall competition footer |u=17 December 2008 }}\n<!--FIXED AND UPGRADED TO fb overall2 competition. FOR DETAILS ON THE PARAMETERS, SEE Template:Fb overall2 competition-->\n\n===Super League Greece===\n\n====Classification====\n{{:2008\u201309 Superleague Greece|transcludesection=Regular season|showteam=OLY}}\n\n==== Results summary ====\n<!-- Instructions are inside each template -->\n{{Fb_rs |hw=13 |hd=1 |hl=1 |hgf=33 |hga=8 |aw=9 |ad=4 |al=2 |agf=17 |aga=6 }}\n{{Fb rs footer|u=April 26, 2009 |s=[http://www.superleaguegreece.net/rankfull.htm Super League Greece] |date=June 2009}}\n\n====Results by round====\n{{#invoke:sports rbr table|table|legendpos=b\n|header=Round\n|label1= Ground\n| res1=H/A/H/A/H/H/A/H/A/H/A/H/H/A/H/A/H/A/H/A/A/H/A/H/A/H/A/A/H/A\n|label2= Result\n| res2=W/W/W/D/W/W/L/W/D/W