mpiacos]]\n|goals1= Triantafyllou {{goal|30}}{{goal|66}}\n|goals2= [[Oscar Gonz\u00e1lez Marcos|\u00d3scar]] {{goal|14}}<br>[[Diogo Lu\u00eds Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|67}}<br>[[Darko Kova\u010devi\u0107|Kova\u010devi\u0107]] {{goal|84}}\n|stadium= Diagoras Stadium\n|location= [[Rhodes (city)|Rhodes]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W\n}}\n\n====Fifth round====\n{{footballbox collapsible \n|date= 21 January 2009\n|time=\n|team1= [[OFI Crete F.C.|OFI]] \n|score= 0 &ndash; 2\n|report=\n|team2= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2= [[Fernando Belluschi|Belluschi]] {{goal|69}}<br/>[[Luciano Galletti|Galetti]] {{goal|85}}\n|stadium= [[Pankritio Stadium]]\n|location= [[Heraklion]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W\n}}\n\n====Quarter-finals====\n{{footballbox collapsible \n|date= 4 February 2009\n|time= 21:15\n|team1= [[PAOK F.C.|PAOK]]\n|score= 1 &ndash; 0\n|team2= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1= [[S\u00e9rgio Concei\u00e7\u00e3o]] {{goal|30}}\n|goals2= \n|stadium= [[Toumba Stadium]]\n|location= [[Thessaloniki]]\n|referee= T. Kakos\n|result= L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible \n|date= 4 March 2009\n|time= 21:15\n|team1= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|score= 2 &ndash; 0\n|aet = yes\n|team2= [[PAOK F.C.|PAOK]]\n|goals1= [[Diogo Luis Santo|Diogo]]{{goal|46}}<br />[[Matt Derbyshire|Derbyshire]]{{goal|110}}\n|goals2= \n|stadium= [[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location= [[Piraeus]]\n|referee= M. Koukoulakis\n|result= W\n}}\n''Olympiacos won 2\u20131 on aggregate.''\n\n====Semi-finals====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 18 March 2009\n|time= 21:15\n|team1= [[Asteras Tripolis F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]]\n|score= 2 &ndash; 2\n|team2= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1= [[Lucio Filomeno|Filomeno]] {{goal|30||35}}\n|goals2= [[Diogo Luis Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|43||73}}\n|stadium= [[Asteras Tripolis Stadium]]\n|location= [[Tripoli, Greece|Tripoli]]\n|referee= D. Kalopoulos\n|result= D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 9 April 2009\n|time= 18:00\n|team1= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|score= 2 &ndash; 1\n|team2= [[Asteras Tripolis F.C.|Asteras Tripoli]]\n|goals1= [[Sebasti\u00e1n Leto|Leto]] {{goal|47}}<br />[[Diogo Luis Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|62}}\n|goals2= [[Danijel Cesarec|Cesarec]] {{goal|39}}\n|stadium= [[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location= [[Piraeus]]\n|referee= G. Daloukas \n|result= W\n}}\n''Olympiacos won 4\u20133 on aggregate.''\n\n====Final====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 2 May 2009\n|time= 20:30\n|team1= [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n|score= 4 &ndash; 4\n|aet = yes\n|report= [http://www.epo.gr/vodafon/detail.asp?e_article_id=14458&e_article_cat_id=4 Report] {{in lang|el}}<br />[http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/association=gre/news/newsid=826219.html Report] \n|team2= [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1= [[Ismael Blanco|Blanco]] {{goal|4||8}}<br /> [[Ignacio Scocco|Scocco]] {{goal|90||107}}\n|goals2= [[Matt Derbyshire|Derbyshire]] {{goal|47||90+6}}<br /> [[Dudu Cearense]] {{goal|72}}<br /> [[Luciano Galletti|Galletti]] {{goal|102}}\n|stadium= [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Olympic Stadium]]\n|location= [[Athens]]\n|attendance= 48,594\n|referee= Anastasios Kakos\n|penalties1=[[Pantelis Kafes|Kafes]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Ismael Blanco|Blanco]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Ignacio Scocco|Scocco]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Arnaldo Edi Lopes da Silva|Edinho]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Daniel Majstorovi\u0107|Majstorovi\u0107]] {{penmiss}}<br />[[Tamandani Nsaliwa|Nsaliwa]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Sebasti\u00e1n Saja|Saja]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Agust\u00edn Pelletieri|Pelletieri]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Nikolaos Georgeas|Georgeas]]{{penmiss}}<br />[[Pantelis Kafes|Kafes]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Ismael Blanco|Blanco]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Ignacio Scocco|Scocco]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Arnaldo Edi Lopes da Silva|Edinho]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Daniel Majstorovi\u0107|Majstorovi\u0107]] {{pengoal}}<br>[[Tamandani Nsaliwa|Nsaliwa]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Sebasti\u00e1n Saja|Saja]] {{pengoal}}<br />[[Agust\u00edn Pelletieri|Pelletieri]] {{penmiss}}\n|penaltyscore=14 &ndash; 15\n|penalties2={{pengoal}} [[Oscar Gonz\u00e1lez Marcos|\u00d3scar]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Dudu Cearense]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Diogo Luis Santo|Diogo]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Didier Domi|Domi]]<br />{{penmiss}} [[Predrag \u0110or\u0111evi\u0107|\u0110or\u0111evi\u0107]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Vasilis Torosidis|Torosidis]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Fernando Belluschi|Belluschi]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Antonis Nikopolidis|Nikopolidis]]<br />{{penmiss}} [[Paraskevas Antzas|Antzas]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Oscar Gonz\u00e1lez Marcos|\u00d3scar]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Dudu Cearense]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Diogo Luis Santo|Diogo]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Didier Domi|Domi]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Predrag \u0110or\u0111evi\u0107|\u0110or\u0111evi\u0107]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Vasilis Torosidis|Torosidis]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Fernando Belluschi|Belluschi]]<br />{{pengoal}} [[Antonis Nikopolidis|Nikopolidis]]\n|result= D\n}}\n\n===[[2008\u201309 UEFA Champions League|UEFA Champions League]]===\n''All times at [[Central European Time|CET]]''\n\n====Third qualifying round====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=13 August 2008\n|time=20:00\n|team1=[[Anorthosis Famagusta FC|Anorthosis]] {{flagicon|CYP}} \n|score=3 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2009/matches/round=15275/match=303812/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|GRE}} [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] \n|goals1=[[Vasilis Torosidis|Torosidis]] {{goal|4|o.g.}}<br>[[\u0141ukasz Sosin|Sosin]] {{goal|17}}<br>[[Vincent Laban|Laban]] {{goal|85}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Antonis Papadopoulos Stadium]]\n|location=[[Larnaca]], [[Cyprus]]\n|attendance=10,500\n|referee=[[Oleg\u00e1rio Benqueren\u00e7a]] ([[Portugal]])\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=27 August 2008\n|time=20:00\n|team1=[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] {{flagicon|GRE}}\n|score=1 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2009/matches/round=15275/match=303828/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|CYP}} [[Anorthosis Famagusta F.C.|Anorthosis]]\n|goals1=[[Fernando Belluschi|Belluschi]] {{goal|54}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location=[[Piraeus]], [[Greece]]\n|attendance=27,904\n|referee=[[Herbert Fandel]] ([[Germany]])\n|result=W\n}}\n''Anorthosis won 3\u20131 on aggregate.''\n\n===[[2008\u201309 UEFA Cup|UEFA Cup]]===\n''All times at [[Central European Time|CET]]''\n\n====First round====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=16 September 2008\n|time=20:00\n|team1=[[FC Nordsj\u00e6lland|Nordsj\u00e6lland]] {{flagicon|DEN}} \n|score=0 &ndash; 2\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15284/match=303952/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|GRE}} [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1=\n|goals2=[[Konstantinos Mitroglou|Mitroglou]] {{goal|74}}<br>[[Sebasti\u00e1n Leto|Leto]] {{goal|90+3}}\n|stadium=[[Farum Park]]\n|location=[[Farum]], [[Denmark]]\n|attendance=5,184\n|referee= Stefan Messner ([[Austria]])\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=2 October 2008\n|time=20:45\n|team1=[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] {{flagicon|GRE}} \n|score=5 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15284/match=303992/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|DEN}} [[FC Nordsj\u00e6lland|Nordsj\u00e6lland]]\n|goals1=[[Vasilis Torosidis|Torosidis]] {{goal|11}}<br>[[Diogo Lu\u00eds Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|30||43}}<br>[[Darko Kova\u010devi\u0107|Kova\u010devi\u0107]] {{goal|72||80}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location=[[Piraeus]], [[Greece]]\n|attendance=24,515\n|referee= Igor Egorov ([[Russia]])\n|result=W\n}}\n''Olympiacos won 7\u20130 on aggregate.''\n\n====Group stage====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=23 October 2008\n|time=20:15\n|team1=[[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray]] {{flagicon|TUR}}\n|score=1 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15285/match=304171/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|GRE}} [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1=[[Harry Kewell|Kewell]] {{goal|25}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Ali Sami Yen Stadium]]\n|location=[[Istanbul]], [[Turkey]]\n|attendance=23,500\n|referee=[[Eduardo Iturralde Gonz\u00e1lez]] ([[Spain]])\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=27 November 2008\n|time=20:45\n|team1=[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] {{flagicon|GRE}} \n|score=5 &ndash; 1\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15285/match=304202/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|POR}} [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]\n|goals1=[[Luciano Galletti|Galletti]] {{goal|1}}<br>[[Christos Patsatzoglou|Patsatzoglou]] {{goal|17}}<br>[[Diogo Lu\u00eds Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|24||53}}<br>[[Fernando Belluschi|Belluschi]] {{goal|44}}\n|goals2=[[David Luiz]] {{goal|33}}\n|stadium=[[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location=[[Piraeus]], [[Greece]]\n|attendance=30,185\n|referee=St\u00e9phane Lannoy ([[France]])\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible \n|date=3 December 2008\n|time=20:45\n|team1=[[FC Metalist Kharkiv|Metalist Kharkiv]] {{flagicon|UKR}} \n|score=1 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15285/match=304218/report=rp.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|GRE}} [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|goals1=[[Edmar Aparecida|Edmar]] {{goal|88}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Metalist Stadium]]\n|location=[[Kharkiv]], [[Ukraine]]\n|attendance=25,000\n|referee=William Collum ([[Scotland]])\n|result=L\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date=18 December 2008\n|time=20:45\n|team1=[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] {{flagicon|GRE}} \n|score=4 &ndash; 0\n|report=[http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2009/matches/round=15285/match=304242/index.html (Report)]\n|team2={{flagicon|GER}} [[Hertha BSC]]\n|goals1=[[Dudu Cearense|Dudu]] {{goal|55}}<br>[[Luciano Galletti|Galletti]] {{goal|68|pen.}}<br>[[Vasilis Torosidis|Torosidis]] {{goal|87}}<br>[[Diogo Lu\u00eds Santo|Diogo]] {{goal|88}}\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Karaiskakis Stadium]]\n|location=[[Piraeus]], [[Greece]]\n|attendance=30,063\n|referee=[