00716045013/http://isleofman.isle-news.com/ Isle of Man News]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110727082404/http://mhkstheyworkforyou.org/default.aspx Information on the work and duties of Members of the House of Keys]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20121108050329/http://viewfinder.english-heritage.org.uk/search/results.aspx?index=0&mainQuery=&searchType=all&form=basic&theme=&county=ISLE%20OF%20MAN&district=&placeName= Images of the Isle of Man] at the [[English Heritage Archive]]\n\n{{Isle of Man}}\n{{Navboxes\n| list =\n{{Navboxes\n| title = [[File:Gnome-globe.svg|25px]]{{nbsp}}Geographic locale\n| list =\n'''[[Geographic coordinate system|Lat. and Long.]] {{Coord|54|09|N|4|29|W|display=inline}} <span style=\"color: darkblue;\">(Douglas)</span>'''\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = International membership\n| list =\n{{British Isles}}\n{{Celtic nations}}\n{{United Kingdom constituents and affiliations}}\n}}\n{{English official language clickable map}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Man, Isle of}}\n[[Category:Isle of Man| ]]\n[[Category:Islands of the Isle of Man|*]]\n[[Category:British Islands]]\n[[Category:British Isles]]\n[[Category:Celtic nations|Isle]]\n[[Category:Crown dependencies|Isle]]\n[[Category:Dependent territories in Europe|Isle of Man]]\n[[Category:English-speaking countries and territories|Isle]]\n[[Category:Former Norwegian colonies|Isle]]\n[[Category:Island countries|Isle]]\n[[Category:Northern European countries|Isle]]\n[[Category:Western European countries|Isle]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description |Island in the Irish Sea}}\n{{For| the racehorse|Isle of Man (horse)}}\n{{pp-move |small= yes}}\n{{coord|54|14|06|N|04|31|30|W|display=title}}\n{{Use British English|date= July 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date= February 2019}}\n{{Infobox dependency\n| name = Isle of Man\n| native_name = {{nobold|{{native name|gv|Mannin, Ellan Vannin}}}}\n| settlement_type = [[Crown dependencies|Crown dependency]]\n| linking_name = the Isle of Man\n| image_flag = F